   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Themistokles. Diokles, one of the cleruchs from Arsinoe and an old acquaintance of mine, is interested in a certain Egyptian called Paris, belonging to the Oxyrhynchite nome, whom he says Axapes the royal scribe has enrolled in the native soldiery, though he did not use to be [- - -]</ab>
